Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:34.83,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(462,54)}「感觉作为女人却输了」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:36.83,Title,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你已经走投无路了 有川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想要还债的话就只能卖身了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请等一下 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在交出去之前能先让我玩玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说什么呢 这家伙可是男的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}男 的 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不如说正因为是女装少年才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少啰嗦 好了 乖乖照我说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:00:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们霜科高中学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对于本校学生的危机不会坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}的说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们这些家伙 别对大人的事情插嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}钞票鞭笞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}运子飞踢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好可怕 给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚刚真是很危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.96,0:01:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}美…美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恭喜你 从今天起你就是我们学生会的一员了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}完全不明所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所谓霜科高中学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是把符合我们眼光的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作为学生会干事招募进来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以说你合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦 这样的话是办不到的 因为我是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不不不 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是说那里长着邪恶的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}邪恶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}像你这样的美少女 怎么可能会是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}男的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的是男孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}感觉作为女人却输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么明明是男孩子却打扮成这种让人误会的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚才的那些人硬让我穿上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说是要把我卖给一些有特殊癖好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看来是有隐情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的双亲全年都游荡于海外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跑到哪就在哪里负债
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且还都是以我的名义欠下的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才会被那些可怕的人追债
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么啊 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的债务就由我们学生会来支付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是作为交换条件 你接下来的高中生活就穿着女装度过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作为学生会的忠犬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}犬…那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊嘞…难道说想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的好吗 只要稍微穿一下女装就再也不用被可怕的人追债了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是一百万日元的厚度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看啊 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊…大家好 接下来是学生会的通告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们霜科高中学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一直是由我 会长运子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}副会长 18禁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}书记 阿尔贝蒂娜2世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这三人组成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而现如今将有新成员加入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}学生会的忠犬 有川姬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且是个男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶的学生会 又擅自做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请适可而止一点
